    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable, well-maintained vehicle at a great value? This car is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it's been cared for and it shows! The exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs well and is ready for the road. No major issues here \u2014 just a solid, dependable car at an honest price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
