    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in poor condition. The interior has significant wear including heavily worn or damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and visible damage to multiple surfaces and controls. The exterior shows substantial damage including deep scratches, multiple dents, and areas of paint damage or rust. Mechanical issues may be present. Best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle or those seeking parts.",
      "price": 6000.0,
